Message queue are used to communicate between the processes.
For more details you can google for the same.

msgq_client.c - msgq client application

msgq_server.c - msgq server application

msg_queue.h   - Interface which contains
                mtype, mcmd and struct msgqbuf 

Run `make all` - to build the appications
                 client.out and server.out executables will be created

Run `make clean` - to clean the build
